thread.title: Yasin Mohamed Abdi
thread.title_full: Keepkey reviewed by Yasin Mohamed Abdi

author: Yasin Mohamed Abdi
title: Yasin Mohamed Abdi
text: Well so far so good, really simple and stylish the best looking hardware wallet available on the market. Would defo recommend it. Had to pay a lot to get it but overall a great product. I paid a total of $194 I live in the UK so shipping fees + custom fees it was a bit frustrating. Works well with Mycelium software.
